Package: ridgeRegression
Type: Package
Title: A Fast Implementation of Ridge Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yueying Hu
Maintainer: Yueying Hu <yueyingh@umich.edu>
Description: A fast tool for calculating coefficients in multiple linear 
              regression with L2 regularization and no intercept term, 
              where independent variables are highly correlated.
